                            Your targeting system glitched, try again.
                            You only moved the decimal 25 places instead of 35.
                        </p>
                    </feedback>
                </choice>

                <choice correct="no">
                    <statement>
                        <p>
                            160000000000000000000000000000000000
                        </p>
                    </statement>

                    <feedback>
                        <p>
                            Your enchanted click missed the mark, try again.
                            Recall that if the exponent is negative the decimal should move to the left.
                        </p>
